---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Resume – James Ding"
  description="Resume of James Ding — Data Scientist & Analyst. MDSA, University of Calgary. TN visa eligible."
>

  <div class="section container-lg">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-end sm:justify-between gap-4">
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Resume</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-foreground">James Ding</h1>
        <p class="mt-2 text-muted-foreground text-lg">Data Scientist · Analyst</p>
        <span class="mt-3 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full border border-primary/30 bg-primary/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-primary">
          <svg class="h-3 w-3 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0z" />
          </svg>
          TN Visa Eligible · No Sponsorship Required
        </span>
      </div>
      <a
        href="/JamesDing_Resume.pdf"
        download
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-primary px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-primary-foreground shadow hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors self-start sm:self-auto"
      >
        <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3m2 8H7a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h5.586a1 1 0 0 1 .707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 0 1 .293.707V19a2 2 0 0 1-2 2z" />
        </svg>
        Download PDF
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Resume body -->
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-card shadow-sm p-8 sm:p-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto font-sans text-sm text-foreground leading-relaxed">

      <!-- Name + contact -->
      <div class="text-center mb-6 border-b border-border pb-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground">James Ding</h2>
        <p class="mt-1 text-muted-foreground text-xs">
          604-842-6134 &nbsp;|&nbsp;
          <a href="mailto:james@dingjames.com" class="underline hover:text-primary transition-colors">james@dingjames.com</a>
          &nbsp;|&nbsp;
          <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/jam-ding" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline hover:text-primary transition-colors">LinkedIn</a>
          &nbsp;|&nbsp;
          <a href="https://github.com/dingjamma" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline hover:text-primary transition-colors">GitHub</a>
          &nbsp;|&nbsp;
          <a href="https://dingjames.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline hover:text-primary transition-colors">Portfolio</a>
        </p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-muted-foreground text-xs">Calgary, AB · TN Visa Eligible · Relocating to the U.S.</p>
      </div>

<!-- Work Experience -->
      <section class="mb-6">
        <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-foreground border-b border-border pb-1 mb-4">Work Experience</h3>

        <div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline">
            <span class="font-bold text-foreground">Associate Data Analyst</span>
            <span class="text-muted-foreground text-xs whitespace-nowrap">May 2025 – Present</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline mb-2">
            <span class="text-primary text-xs font-medium">AirSprint Inc.</span>
            <span class="text-muted-foreground text-xs">Calgary, AB</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-muted-foreground">
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="mt-1.5 h-1 w-1 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-muted-foreground/60"></span><span>Conducted EDA on 12 years of flight operations data across 78K+ flights to identify key demand drivers, seasonality factors, and a COVID-era regime shift informing model design</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="mt-1.5 h-1 w-1 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-muted-foreground/60"></span><span>Built and deployed a Prophet time-series forecasting model achieving 10% weekly / 7% monthly MAPE in backtesting and 6% weekly / 2% monthly MAPE in live 2026 production, targeting 1%+ reduction in $49M annual empty leg positioning costs</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="mt-1.5 h-1 w-1 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-muted-foreground/60"></span><span>Built automated data ingestion pipelines (FL3XX, Salesforce, Foreflight → AWS Lambda → S3 → Snowflake) with end-to-end data quality monitoring and alerting</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="mt-1.5 h-1 w-1 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-muted-foreground/60"></span><span>Designed a data-driven RBAC workaround for FL3XX's booking platform by building a cleansing and segmentation pipeline with custom business logic mapping user roles (owner, individual, full access) and a manual override layer to manage edge cases</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="mt-1.5 h-1 w-1 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-muted-foreground/60"></span><span>Built QuickSight dashboards enabling real-time monitoring of operational KPIs, flight demand trends, and fleet utilization for executive and operational stakeholders</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Projects -->
      <section class="mb-6">
        <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-foreground border-b border-border pb-1 mb-4">Projects</h3>

        <!-- Calgary Housing -->
        <div class="mb-4">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline">
            <span class="font-bold text-foreground">Calgary Housing Price Predictor</span>
            <span class="text-muted-foreground text-xs whitespace-nowrap">Mar 2026</span>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-2 flex gap-3">
            <a href="https://github.com/dingjamma/Calgary-Housing" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary text-xs hover:underline">github.com/dingjamma/Calgary-Housing</a>
            <span class="text-muted-foreground text-xs">·</span>
            <a href="https://calgary-housing-7phh7dhjyyd2r7mtjymuvm.streamlit.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary text-xs hover:underline">Live Dashboard</a>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-muted-foreground">
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="mt-1.5 h-1 w-1 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-muted-foreground/60"></span><span>Fully automated pipeline scraping 21 years of housing, oil, and economic data; trained three XGBoost models (annual, monthly, daily) with a live Housing Pressure Score deployed on Streamlit</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="mt-1.5 h-1 w-1 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-muted-foreground/60"></span><span>Built an intelligence layer — live news scraper (CBC, OilPrice, Better Dwelling) and auto-generated market reports, automated biweekly via GitHub Actions</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="mt-1.5 h-1 w-1 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-muted-foreground/60"></span><span>Integrated MiroFish multi-agent geopolitical simulation (8 AI actors: BoC, OPEC+, Iran/IRGC, Alberta energy, Calgary buyers) using OASIS, CAMEL-AI, and GraphRAG (Zep) to predict December 2026 housing outcomes</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Education -->
      <section class="mb-6">
        <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-foreground border-b border-border pb-1 mb-4">Education</h3>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline">
            <div>
              <span class="font-bold text-foreground">Master of Data Science & Analytics</span>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground text-xs">University of Calgary</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-right">
              <span class="text-muted-foreground text-xs whitespace-nowrap">Dec 2025</span>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground text-xs">Calgary, AB</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline">
            <div>
              <span class="font-bold text-foreground">Bachelor of Science, Agriculture Commerce</span>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground text-xs">University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-right">
              <span class="text-muted-foreground text-xs whitespace-nowrap">May 2016</span>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground text-xs">Champaign, IL</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Technical Skills -->
      <section>
        <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-foreground border-b border-border pb-1 mb-3">Technical Skills</h3>
        <div class="space-y-1.5 text-muted-foreground">
          <p><span class="font-semibold text-foreground">Languages:</span> Python, SQL, R, JavaScript</p>
          <p><span class="font-semibold text-foreground">Machine Learning:</span> XGBoost, Random Forest, scikit-learn, time-series forecasting, classification, feature engineering</p>
          <p><span class="font-semibold text-foreground">Deep Learning:</span> PyTorch, TensorFlow, Hugging Face, CNNs, LSTMs, Reinforcement Learning (PPO)</p>
          <p><span class="font-semibold text-foreground">Statistics:</span> A/B testing, experimental design, hypothesis testing, regression</p>
          <p><span class="font-semibold text-foreground">Platforms:</span> AWS (Lambda, S3, Bedrock, QuickSight, AppFlow, EventBridge, OpenSearch, API Gateway, CDK), Snowflake, Vercel, Streamlit, Git, GitHub Actions</p>
          <p><span class="font-semibold text-foreground">AI/LLMs:</span> Multi-agent simulation (OASIS, CAMEL-AI), GraphRAG (Zep), LLM application development (RAG, prompt engineering, tool use, agent design), OpenAI-compatible APIs</p>
        </div>
      </section>

    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>
